special election shall be held to select a full-time student member. The elected student member shall serve for
the remainder of the unexpired term.
(3) The faculty member and staff member shall serve one (1) year terms and cease to be eligible for membership
on the board of trustees upon termination of their respective relationships with, or leadership positions within,
