to carry out its primary function to periodically evaluate the institution's progress in implementing its mission,
goals, and objectives to conform to the strategic agenda, or to otherwise perform its duties under KRS 164.830
shall be cause for the Governor to remove all appointed members of the board and replace the entire appointed
