appointed to serve the remainder of an unexpired term,[this meeting] there shall be elected a vice chairperson and a
secretary for the board. Each board shall appoint a treasurer, and such officers as it deems necessary, but no member
of any of the boards shall be appointed treasurer. No member of any board shall draw any salary for his or her

CHAPTER 171 13
services, but shall be reimbursed for necessary expenditures made in going to and from each meeting of the board and
